episodes.title: Investigating the most Dangerous Cult in Jiu Jitsu
episodes.description:
in this video I visited Garami Jiu Jitsu in Fayettville North Carolina. There have been rumors about this gym potentially being a cult, so I went to find out for myself and see if Garami is a legit Jiu Jitsu gym, or a place to stay away from.
